{"tid":1762723,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MOMOLAND妍雨、泰河宣佈退團！ 公司預告「還有第三個成員」商討中","createTime":"2019-11-29T19:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T16:52:34.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fe73550b5e4ce5845f929458529aca0207d2578c","tid":1762723,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:15:59.000Z","msg":"南韓大勢(?)女團MOMOLAND以一曲《BBoom BBoom》爆紅，更是眾多年末節目爭相邀請的熱門偶像。不過30日凌晨，經紀公司「MLD娛樂」突然宣布人氣成員妍雨和泰河退團，另一名成員Daisy則「雙方仍在商討中」，在粉絲圈丟下震撼彈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4314/d4314854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4314%2Fd4314854.jpg&h=7bb1a1b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲妍雨宣佈退出MOMOLAND。（圖／翻攝自MOMOLAND臉書）<br />\n<br />\nMOMOLAND妍雨因長相秀麗、出眾，特別受到喜愛，是隊中的人氣成員。今年六月她就因將近1個月沒有參與MOMOLAND行程，而傳出退隊傳聞，當時公司還特別澄清「關於妍雨退團的傳聞絕對不是事實」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4544/d4544678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4544%2Fd4544678.jpg&h=5d416ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMOLAND成員泰河宣佈退團。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n不過事隔將近半年，MOMOLAND終究沒有留下妍雨。經紀公司「MLD娛樂」30日透過公告宣布，妍雨因為難以兼顧歌手和演員的行程，決定退隊，「今後將會繼續留在公司作為演員活動」。泰河則是已經解約，經紀公司強調：「（泰河）本人也苦惱已久，但公司仍舊尊重本人意願，會繼續為泰河的新開始應援。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4217/d4217864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4217%2Fd4217864.jpg&h=8230f92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMOLAND將暫時以六人體活動。（圖／翻攝自推特／MMLD_Official）<br />\n<br />\n至於先前曾爆出戀愛傳聞的Daisy，去留則「仍在與公司商討當中」，結果待定後公司將再次告知，而目前MOMOLAND將暫時以六人女團的形式活動。不過由於妍雨和Daisy都是隊中人氣成員，而泰河則是主唱，消息一出後讓不少粉絲擔心說：「雖然六人體一段時間了，但好難想像MOMOLAND之後會變成怎樣。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3895/d3895581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3895%2Fd3895581.jpg&h=a922279d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMOLAND成員Daisy的去留「正在和公司商討中」。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n妍雨阿....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一早話左收硬皮架啦"},{"pid":"c93e2f7331976a818e86cc71fc8173086f5d39ba","tid":1762723,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 導狗3點幾都唔能洗訓?"},{"pid":"6e8bc0287692d89e9c3cd3a2e4dd0f04cd4a1b69","tid":1762723,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:21:42.000Z","msg":"今晚咁夜牙=="},{"pid":"326ee5971721702b2d295fe9c9838b268c024eb9","tid":1762723,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93e2f7331976a818e86cc71fc8173086f5d39ba","tid":1762723,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 導狗3點幾都唔能洗訓?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"你件垃圾都未撚訓啦"},{"pid":"bc0b54c5380e73ecbf1f6bd6d22f80819ac46df9","tid":1762723,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"326ee5971721702b2d295fe9c9838b268c024eb9","tid":1762723,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93e2f7331976a818e86cc71fc8173086f5d39ba","tid":1762723,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 導狗3點幾都唔能洗訓?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"你件垃圾都未撚訓啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"= =捕緊牙笠4點上水"},{"pid":"f17c43b2020b2a67f8422a5fa6ea9f3b10559a00","tid":1762723,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc0b54c5380e73ecbf1f6bd6d22f80819ac46df9","tid":1762723,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"326ee5971721702b2d295fe9c9838b268c024eb9","tid":1762723,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93e2f7331976a818e86cc71fc8173086f5d39ba","tid":1762723,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"屌奶星 導狗3點幾都唔能洗訓?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"你件垃圾都未撚訓啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"= =捕緊牙笠4點上水"},"citedBy":